    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "God Himself",
      "uuid": "ab987ad3773144f5a5d0cd8fa9b8845f",
      "x": -171.18627374382697,
      "y": 881.2885606279569,
      "width": 324.8517457246961,
      "height": 360.0,
      "z_value": 10.0,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Our faith in him, and the holy spirit which encumbers.\n\nThere are two sides of this tale that we can never tell \nWithout considering the other, \nThis immaculate bond \nBetween those who pursue answers \nAnd those who possess them,\nBoth must be discussed in equal value.\n\nThose are in effect the same, one being \nThe manifestation of the concept of God, \n\nGlory, Kindness, and Truth, \n\nWhile the counterpart being the human manifestation of such\n"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Practical and pleasurable",
      "uuid": "85a37240acd742d08ba44be616b4300f",
      "x": 1245.737662706578,
      "y": -1432.9482384223134,
      "width": 300.3786091418867,
      "height": 148.79518348087413,
      "z_value": -9.91000000000005,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd\">\n<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /><style type=\"text/css\">\np, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\nhr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }\nli.unchecked::marker { content: \"\\2610\"; }\nli.checked::marker { content: \"\\2612\"; }\n</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Segoe UI'; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Power sixth I call to us</p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">I call on truth and error flees</p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Twelve in one number of one nature</p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Make promise to keep silence on Thy Virtue</p></body></html>"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Kinetic",
      "uuid": "cdaafe4abeea48deb0a651f15be54b43",
      "x": 528.9855072463772,
      "y": -650.7246376811594,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.926000000000041,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "And confirm his plan did indeed work quite fine by adding into this the context of Genesis 3:22\n\nAnd the lord God said \n\"look! The man who now become like one of us\""
    },
